    "4006911": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan's Mother",
                    "T": "The reason the birds sing so sweetly is because they drink the spring water from up on mountaintops. Xinyan, we're not singers in this family, none of us are. What makes you think you can be any different?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Oh, so I just need to go drink some of this spring water, and then I'll be able to sing? I'll be right back, Mama!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4006920": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan's Father",
                    "T": "You mustn't stay out so late in the mountains by yourself, child! You scared the bejesus out of me! ...Here, this is the spring water you were looking for."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Really? Oh, you're the best, daddy!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4006921": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan's Mother",
                    "T": "Where did she run off to this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan's Father",
                    "T": "To find somewhere she could sing, no doubt. *sigh* She can't be persuaded, and we can't stop her from walking out the door. Did you really have to lie to her like that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan's Mother",
                    "T": "How was I supposed to know she'd go running off looking for spring water! *sigh* When is she going to come to her senses..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4006922": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Dock Worker",
                    "T": "Get down from there! You can't set up a stage here! If you can't sing, you should be keeping your mouth shut, not putting on a public performance! Ugh."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Aaaah, don't tear down the stage!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4006916": {
        "Desc": "Approach the doors from which you hear voices",
        "Step": "After drinking the spring water you found for her and recovering her voice, the fiery flower named \"Blazing Heart\" sends you and the others to the hall of music. The city in the mirage is strikingly similar to Liyue Harbor...",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "4006904": {
        "Desc": "Approach the doors from which you hear voices",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Uncle Zhu",
                    "T": "Xinyan, my dear child, why are you playing that crass instrument again? It's not ladylike."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jixiang",
                    "T": "Oh, Xinyan, your mother has asked me to teach you some embroidery when I can find the time. It's an elegant and enjoyable craft. Just come to Auntie's house whenever you're free."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Uncle Hai",
                    "T": "Quit making that racket by the side of the road! If you have to play, play something classy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wh—Why are they being so mean!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Ugh, these people..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "ARGH! That's it! Why are you not yelling back? What happened to your rock 'n' roll spirit?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Hehe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And now you're laughing!? Aren't you mad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Sometimes it's hard to get mad when you hear the same thing a hundred times. Still... thanks, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Uh what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Auntie Jixiang, how are you doing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jixiang",
                    "T": "Oh, dear child, I've been waiting to hear from you for a long time. This weekend, I'll be free..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Auntie, stop thinking about me for a hot sec, your stove is still on, and you're cooking soup, right? Hmm... you see, it's all burnt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jixiang",
                    "T": "Oh! How did this happen!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Oh my, Uncle Zhu, Little Zhu is playing in the mud by the river again! Didn't you tell him to not do that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Uncle Zhu",
                    "T": "What? That rascal is up to his old shenanigans behind my back again, is he? Oh, well, we'll see about that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Hehehe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Sorry, Uncle Hai, I'll move my stage someplace else. But, your musical taste needs to evolve if you wanna keep up with the times."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Maybe you didn't know, but even the most famous opera singer in Liyue likes listening to my boorish music."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Uncle Hai",
                    "T": "What did you say? Is that true? You're not making this up, are you? Huh, I'll have to look into this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "They're all gone..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "See? Knowing the right words to say and when to smile can solve almost any problem."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "If that's the case, then what's your rock 'n' roll spirit for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "My rock 'n' roll spirit isn't something I just use to win an argument. That'd be a real waste."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Rock 'n' roll is a revolution! Transforming your identity and destiny, saying goodbye to concessions and cowardice... it does them all. And most importantly, it lets you do it with art rather than words!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "My rock 'n' roll has an unbreakable spirit, like a flame in a rainstorm that refuses to go out, or the magma that never stops boiling under the surface of the land."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Okay, let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Let's go that way! There's a side path right there."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
